=== 招聘信息 ===
 
 公司名称:昆泰集成电路(上海)有限公司 
 招聘职位:模拟设计工程师（Analog Design Engineer）  
 截至日期:2005-11-10  
 最低学历:本科  
 招聘人数:人 
 工作地点: 上海   
 简历投递处: http://www.jobmm.com/company_add/Kuntai_job.asp
 
岗位描述: 
 
职责：
1、晶体管级、高速/射频模拟电路设计、测试与评估
2、功放、数模转换、锁相环等设计
3、与后端工程师、销售工程师及测试工程师进行产品市场化合作
Job Description
1、Circuit designer responsible for transistor level design 
   of high speed and RF analog circuits, product evaluation and
   characterization.
2、Duties also include design of amplifiers, mixers, D/A and
   A/D converters, PLLs
3、Developing engineering specifications and work with Mask
   Design, Applications Engineering, Product Engineering and
   Test Engineering to successfully bring products to market.
 
相关要求: 
 
要求：
1、电子、计算机及相关专业学士学位（硕士优先）
2、良好的英语听、说、读、写能力
3、有一定的模拟CMOS集成电路设计经验
4、熟悉晶体管、CMOS、功放、偏置电路、数模/模数转换器
5、有高速数模转换、锁相环及高速发射/接收相关方面设计经验者优先
Job Requirements
Requires BSEE and 2+ years of experience in analog CMOS IC
design or MSEE, and knowledge of transistor equations,
CMOS amplifier design, biasing methods and analog to
digital conversion techniques. Experience in high speed 
A/D conversion, PLLs and high speed transmitter/receiver 
design is a plus.
  
